table.table.table-striped
  each user in list
    - var name = [user.firstname, user.lastname].join(' ')
    tr
      td
        div(data-status_user_id=user.id, class=user.online ? "online" : "")
          img(src="/user/avatar/thumbnail/"+ user.id, width="60", height="60", alt=name)
      td.vmiddle= name
      td.vmiddle
        a.request(href="#", data-id=user.id) Добавить в друзья
